snippet.title: Sid Meier's C.P.U. Bach (3DO) - Opening & Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here is a video from Sid Meier's C.P.U. Bach for the 3DO. The game was an educational title that had you composing your own musical symphonies...

This video contains the opening cinema as well as 2 user-created pieces..
